rms of muscle focus is how the belt squats affect your glutes.</div></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1666254290035" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1666254290035" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg Handstands" data-exc="Handstands"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/866d651d-d8ad-432c-8482-cef202f55af5/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Belt-Squat-Exercise.jpg" alt="Belt Squat Exercise" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1200" height="800" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="Belt Squat Exercise" natural-width="1200" natural-height="800"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1658550677203" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1658550677203"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 800px !important; height: 53px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 400px 26.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 800px !important; height: 53px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-567677" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000"><span style="caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1. Quadriceps</span></font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1658550684040" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1658550684040"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" style=